description: Uses the Bing Search API to return web search results.
credential: github.com/gptscript-ai/search/bing-credential

arg: q: (required) The search query to use.
arg: country: (optional) The country to use for the search in ISO 3166-2 format.
arg: search_lang: (optional) An RFC 5646 language code to use for the search. This will be used in the Accept-Language header.
arg: offset: (optional) The offset to use for the search results (used for pagination).

#!${GPTSCRIPT_TOOL_DIR}/bin/gptscript-go-tool "${GPTSCRIPT_INPUT}"
